The article is a statement issued by the United States on May 2, 2019, to commemorate the 77th Anniversary of the Battle of the Coral Sea. The statement expresses greetings to the people of Australia and acknowledges the joint efforts of American and Australian naval and air forces in protecting shared values of freedom and democracy during the battle. It highlights the strong relationship between the United States and Australia, which has contributed to promoting peace and prosperity globally for over a century. The statement also pays tribute to the heroic defenders who sacrificed their lives for freedom and expresses gratitude on behalf of the nations and the world.